From: jepler@nyx.cs.du.edu (Jeff Epler)
Subject: POVRAY executables at Sunsite
Date: Sun, 29 Aug 93 00:41:04 GMT

I've uploaded the binary for POVray 1.0 to Sunsite.  It is currently
in the directory /pub/Linux/Incoming and is named
povray-1.0.linux.tar.gz

This version was compiled with support for displaying a render in
progress under X and for this reason will likely fail to run if you
don't have the X libs.

Please mail me if there are any problems with the exectuable.  Please
ask in an appropriate newsgroup if you have any more general question
about povray.  (comp.graphics is a good place to start.  Also, the faq
there probably has a pointer to the "dkb-l" mailing list. This list
discusses povray also.  (dkb is it's parent program)


